Package fingerprint_recognition

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Data
    Data class represent input data for the network.
    Driver
    Driver class is responsible for running the application.
    GraphicsProcessor
    Graphics processor responsible for processing input images to a form which can be processed by the neural network.
    Layer
    Layer class represents a layer in a neural network.
    Node
    Mode class represents a single neuron in a neural network.
    ParamsManager
    ParamsManager class is responsible for parsing and rendering command line arguments accessible.
    Perceptron
    Perceptron class represents the structure of the neural network.
    SharedTypes
    SharedTypes class is used to store all data structures and variables shared among other classes.
    TrainingData
    TrainingData class represents a piece of training data.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    SharedTypes.LayerType
    Enum type representing type of the network's layer.
